anyathā tadutthāpite kāyavāgvijñapty api saṃkliṣṭe syātām. ato bahirindriyavyāpāravikalpāv upasaṃhṛtya sthātavyaṃ kāṣṭhavat tadā. sarvavyāpāravirahān nirvyāpārāḥ sarvadharmā iti manasi nidhāya.

<commentary>aparam āha.

uddhatam iti saddharmādiśravaṇapramādād api uddhatam, vikṣepabahulam ity arthaḥ. sopahāsaṃ vāgviheṭhanārambhakaṃ tayā yuktaṃ vā. mānaś cittasyonnatiḥ. madaḥ svadharme cittasyābhiniveśaḥ. tābhyām anvitaṃ tatsaṃprayuktam. utprāsaḥ kāyikī viheṭhanā. tena sahotkaṭam. vakraṃ kuṭilaṃ śaṭhaṃ vā. vañcakaṃ pratārakaṃ māyāvi vā. yadi mano bhavet, sthātavyaṃ kāṣṭhavat tadeti saṃbandhaḥ.</commentary>

ātmotkarṣaṇaṃ svaguṇātiśayaprakāśanam. tadābhāsaṃ tatpratibhāsaṃ tadvikalpanāt. parapaṃsanaṃ paravigrahaḥ doṣāviṣkaraṇaṃ vā, tadyuktam.